---
title: Southern Chicken Schnitzels & Potato Wedges with Creamy Rainbow Slaw
description: Golden crusted chicken schnitzels get a boost of flavour with a sweet mustard spice blend! Serve up a side of potato wedges plus
a crisp and colourful slaw for a bright and tasty dinner that brings fun and flavour to the table.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-schnitzel-kumara-wedges-68440fe8.jpg
